{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.1","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:1","prev_osis_id":"Neh.003.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les travaux poursuivis, malgr\u00e9 les obstacles que suscitent les ennemis des Juifs<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-23: cf. N\u00e9 2:18-20. (Esd 4:4, 5; 5:1-5.) Ps 123; 124.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Lorsque Sanballat apprit que nous reb\u00e2tissions la muraille, il fut en col\u00e8re et tr\u00e8s irrit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.2","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.3.32","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 3:32","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.3.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.2","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:2","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il se moqua des Juifs, et dit devant ses fr\u00e8res et devant les soldats de Samarie: A quoi travaillent ces Juifs impuissants? Les laissera-t-on faire? Sacrifieront-ils? Vont-ils achever? Redonneront-ils vie \u00e0 des pierres ensevelies sous des monceaux de poussi\u00e8re et consum\u00e9es par le feu?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.3","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.1","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.3","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:3","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Tobija, l\u2019Ammonite, \u00e9tait \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 de lui, et il dit: Qu\u2019ils b\u00e2tissent seulement! Si un renard s\u2019\u00e9lance, il renversera leur muraille de pierres!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.2","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.4","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:4","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>\u00c9coute, \u00f4 notre Dieu, comme nous sommes m\u00e9pris\u00e9s! Fais retomber leurs insultes sur leur t\u00eate, et livre-les au pillage sur une terre o\u00f9 ils soient captifs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.5","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.3","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.5","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:5","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ne pardonne pas leur iniquit\u00e9, et que leur p\u00e9ch\u00e9 ne soit pas effac\u00e9 de devant toi; car ils ont offens\u00e9 ceux qui b\u00e2tissent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.6","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.6","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:6","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Nous reb\u00e2t\u00eemes la muraille, qui fut partout achev\u00e9e jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la moiti\u00e9 de sa hauteur. Et le peuple prit \u00e0 c\u0153ur ce travail.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.7","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.5","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.7","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:7","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Mais Sanballat, Tobija, les Arabes, les Ammonites et les Asdodiens, furent tr\u00e8s irrit\u00e9s en apprenant que la r\u00e9paration des murs avan\u00e7ait et que les br\u00e8ches commen\u00e7aient \u00e0 se fermer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.8","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.6","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.8","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:8","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Ils se ligu\u00e8rent tous ensemble pour venir attaquer J\u00e9rusalem et lui causer du dommage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.9","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.7","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.9","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:9","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Nous pri\u00e2mes notre Dieu, et nous \u00e9tabl\u00eemes une garde jour et nuit pour nous d\u00e9fendre contre leurs attaques.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.10","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.8","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.10","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:10","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Cependant Juda disait: Les forces manquent \u00e0 ceux qui portent les fardeaux, et les d\u00e9combres sont consid\u00e9rables; nous ne pourrons pas b\u00e2tir la muraille.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.11","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.9","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.11","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:11","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Et nos ennemis disaient: Ils ne sauront et ne verront rien jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que nous arrivions au milieu d\u2019eux; nous les tuerons, et nous ferons ainsi cesser l\u2019ouvrage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.12","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.10","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.12","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:12","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Or les Juifs qui habitaient pr\u00e8s d\u2019eux vinrent dix fois nous avertir, de tous les lieux d\u2019o\u00f9 ils se rendaient vers nous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.13","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.11","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.13","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:13","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi je pla\u00e7ai, dans les enfoncements derri\u00e8re la muraille et sur des terrains secs, le peuple par familles, tous avec leurs \u00e9p\u00e9es, leurs lances et leurs arcs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.14","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.12","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.14","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:14","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Je regardai, et m\u2019\u00e9tant lev\u00e9, je dis aux grands, aux magistrats, et au reste du peuple: Ne les craignez pas! Souvenez-vous du Seigneur, grand et redoutable, et combattez pour vos fr\u00e8res, pour vos fils et vos filles, pour vos femmes et pour vos maisons!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.15","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.13","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.15","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:15","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Lorsque nos ennemis apprirent que nous \u00e9tions avertis, Dieu an\u00e9antit leur projet, et nous retourn\u00e2mes tous \u00e0 la muraille, chacun \u00e0 son ouvrage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.16","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.14","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.16","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:16","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Depuis ce jour, la moiti\u00e9 de mes serviteurs travaillaient, et l\u2019autre moiti\u00e9 \u00e9tait arm\u00e9e de lances, de boucliers, d\u2019arcs et de cuirasses. Les chefs \u00e9taient derri\u00e8re toute la maison de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.17","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.15","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.17","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:17","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Ceux qui b\u00e2tissaient la muraille, et ceux qui portaient ou chargeaient les fardeaux, travaillaient d\u2019une main et tenaient une arme de l\u2019autre;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.18","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.16","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.18","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:18","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>chacun d\u2019eux, en travaillant, avait son \u00e9p\u00e9e ceinte autour des reins. Celui qui sonnait de la trompette se tenait pr\u00e8s de moi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.19","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.17","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.19","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:19","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Je dis aux grands, aux magistrats, et au reste du peuple: L\u2019ouvrage est consid\u00e9rable et \u00e9tendu, et nous sommes dispers\u00e9s sur la muraille, \u00e9loign\u00e9s les uns des autres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.20","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:20","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.18","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.20","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:20","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Au son de la trompette, rassemblez-vous aupr\u00e8s de nous, vers le lieu d\u2019o\u00f9 vous l\u2019entendrez; notre Dieu combattra pour nous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.21","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:21","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.19","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.21","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:21","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>C\u2019est ainsi que nous poursuivions l\u2019ouvrage, la moiti\u00e9 d\u2019entre nous la lance \u00e0 la main depuis le lever de l\u2019aurore jusqu\u2019\u00e0 l\u2019apparition des \u00e9toiles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.22","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:22","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.20","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:20","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.22","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:22","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.004.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Dans ce m\u00eame temps, je dis encore au peuple: Que chacun passe la nuit dans J\u00e9rusalem avec son serviteur; faisons la garde pendant la nuit, et travaillons pendant le jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.23","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:23","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.21","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:21","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.23","label":"","reference":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:23","prev_osis_id":"Neh.004.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Neh.005.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Neh.4.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Et nous ne quittions point nos v\u00eatements, ni moi, ni mes fr\u00e8res, ni mes serviteurs, ni les hommes de garde qui me suivaient; chacun n\u2019avait que ses armes et de l\u2019eau.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Neh.4","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.5.1","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.5.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Neh.4.22","name":"N\u00e9h\u00e9mie 4:22","id":"fra-LSG:Neh.4.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc11ee842.32401327');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc11ee842.32401327\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc11ee842.32401327","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5a